---
---

<section class="wii-channel-era w-full min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-4 md:px-8 bg-[#eef5f8] relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  
  <!-- Ambient floating bubbles -->
  <div class="absolute w-64 h-64 bg-white rounded-full opacity-60 blur-3xl -top-10 left-10 animate-[float-slow_8s_infinite_ease-in-out]"></div>
  <div class="absolute w-96 h-96 bg-blue-100 rounded-full opacity-50 blur-3xl bottom-10 right-10 animate-[float-slow_12s_infinite_ease-in-out_reverse]"></div>
  <div class="absolute w-40 h-40 bg-white rounded-full opacity-40 blur-2xl top-1/2 left-1/2 animate-[float-slow_10s_infinite_ease-in-out]"></div>

  <!-- The "Channel" Window -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl w-full relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Channel Header -->
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center mb-8">
      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md px-16 py-3 rounded-full shadow-[0_4px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border-2 border-white/90">
        <h2 class="text-3xl text-[#5a6b7c] font-bold tracking-wide wii-font">David Channel</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Container -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-stretch justify-center">
      
      <!-- Avatar (The "Mii" Window) -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05),_inset_0_-5px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)] border-[3px] border-white group transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]">
        
        <div class="w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f5f8fa] to-[#e4edf2] rounded-[2.5rem] p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden relative shadow-inner">
           <!-- Grid dot overlay for texture -->
           <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #000 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 10px 10px;"></div>
           
           <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/142668300?v=4" alt="David Schuchert" class="w-48 h-48 sm:w-56 sm:h-56 object-cover rounded-full shadow-[0_15px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] border-8 border-white relative z-10 transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:rotate-3" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Detail Text Box -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-6">
        
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05),_inset_0_-5px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)] border-[3px] border-white flex flex-col justify-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#5a6b7c] mb-6 wii-font">Knowledgesharing als Passion.</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[#738392] text-lg wii-font leading-relaxed font-medium">
            <p>
              Hey! Die Web-Entwicklung kann für Neulinge oft wie ein undurchdringlicher Dschungel wirken. Genau deswegen liebe ich es, Dinge beizubringen.
            </p>
            <p>
              Als Dozent an der DBE-Academy habe ich es mir zur Aufgabe gemacht, komplexe Architekturen und Frameworks wie React oder Laravel so zu erklären, dass sie nicht nur verstanden, sondern auch mit Leidenschaft angewendet werden.
            </p>
            <p>
              Erfahrung wächst am besten, wenn man sie teilt!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Small Button Area -->
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="h-16 w-16 bg-white/90 rounded-full shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#5a6b7c] cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#eaf4fe] transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4ca1ef] to-[#3b8fdc] rounded-full shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(59,143,220,0.3)] border-2 border-white flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
             <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg wii-font">Start</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  /* Emulate standard, soft Nintendo fonts (like Maru Gothic or basic rounded sans) */
  .wii-font {
    font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  }
  
  .wii-channel-era {
    color: #5a6b7c;
  }

  @keyframes float-slow {
    0% { transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); }
    33% { transform: translate(30px, -50px) scale(1.05); }
    66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.95); }
    100% { transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); }
  }
</style>
